DexGrpc
public static final class DexGrpc.DexBlockingStub extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractBlockingStub<DexGrpc.DexBlockingStub>
A stub to allow clients to do synchronous rpc calls to service Dex. 
 Dex represents the dex gRPC service.
